Chinese vaccines.

145
00:07:11,100 --> 00:07:14,240
And that’s why Chinese state-run media wants
you to know:

146
00:07:14,240 --> 00:07:16,940
Chinese vaccines are definitely safe.

147
00:07:16,940 --> 00:07:19,669
“Are China’s vaccines safe?

148
00:07:19,669 --> 00:07:23,660
Amid widespread public concern and questions
from the media

149
00:07:23,660 --> 00:07:25,770
