vaccines around the world.

155
00:07:41,960 --> 00:07:43,120
That sounds...great.

156
00:07:43,120 --> 00:07:48,330
So how do you feel about China’s plan to
sell you vaccines?

157
00:07:48,330 --> 00:07:49,650
